properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 3 at 2:00PM PST until January 5 at 9:00AM PST by NWS San Francisco CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...A moderate chop expected.

* WHERE...San Pablo Bay, Suisun Bay, the West Delta and the San
Francisco Bay north of the Bay Bridge.

* WHEN...From 9 PM Saturday to 9 AM PST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 PM SATURDAY TO 9 AM PST SUNDAY
